#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "What is &i18n-ktouch;?"
msgstr "Šta je &i18n-ktouch;?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-ktouch; is a program for learning to touch type."
msgstr "&i18n-ktouch; je program za učenje kucanja bez gledanja tastature."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; provides you with text to train on and adjusts to different "
"levels depending on how good you are. It shows your keyboard and indicates "
"which key to press next and the correct finger to use."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; Vam daje teks za vježbanje kao i za podešavanje težine u "
"ovisnosti koliko ste dobri. Ono pokazuje koja je naredna tipka koju treba da "
"pritisnete i koji prst koji treba da koristite."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The main screen of &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Glavni zaslon &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The main screen of &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Glavni zaslon &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; is a touch typing tutor aimed mostly at personal use. You "
"learn typing with all fingers, step by step, without having to look down at "
"the keyboard all the time to find the right keys which slows you down a lot."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; je učitelj za kucanje bez gledanja tastature usmjeren uglavnom "
"za privatnu upotrebu. Učite kucati svim prstima, korak po korak, bez potrebe "
"da stalno gledate tastature kako bi pronašli odgovarajuću tipku što vas "
"veoma usporava."

