#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; will show you the first course available for your current "
"keyboard layout."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; će vam pokazati prvi dostupni kurs za vaš trenutni tip "
