#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose your lesson from the list on left of the window. You cannot choose "
"the locked lessons with <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-object-locked.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> as they are too difficult for your current skills. Pass "
"lessons to unlock new ones. The preview of the selected lesson will be shown "
"on the right of lessons list."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite vašu lekciju iz liste u gornjem lijevom dijelu prozora. Ne možete "
"izabrati zaključane lecije sa  <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"Icon-object-locked.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> jer su one preteške za vaš trenutne mogućnosti. Prođite "
"lekcije kako bi ste otključali nove. Pregled odabranih lekcija će biti "
"pokazan na desnom dijelu liste sa lekcijama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More information about the selected course can be shown and hidden again "
"using <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-dialog-"
"information.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"button next to the course title."
msgstr ""
"Više informacija o izabranom smjeru mogu biti ponovo pokazane ili skrivene "
"koristeći <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-dialog-"
"information.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> dugme "
"pored naziva vašeg kursa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you finished with the selection click on <guibutton>Start Training</"
