#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The training screen of &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Zaslon za vježbu &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The training screen of &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Zaslon za vježbu &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Visibility of training screen parts can be configured using <link linkend="
"\"configuration_dialog\">&i18n-ktouch; configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Vidljivost zaslon za vježbu može biti podešena koristeći <link linkend="
"\"configuration_dialog\">&i18n-ktouch; podešavajući dijalog</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Place your two index fingers on the two keys on your keyboard with the two "
"little tactile markers near the center of the middle character row. With "
"that done your other fingers will find their intended keys almost "
"automatically. Your thumbs should rest above the space key, the only key you "
"will ever use them for when touch typing. The other fingers should be placed "
"on the three keys adjacent to the marked keys on the center row. Keys for "
"the same finger are grouped together through their color. Try to move your "
"hands as little as possible and always try to return your fingers to their "
"resting positions after you have typed a character."
msgstr ""
"Stavite svoja dva kažiprsta na dvije tipke tastature sa dva mala osjetna "
"markera pored centra vašeg srednjeg reda karaktera. Nakon što ste to obavili "
"ostali prsti će naći njihove predviđene tikke gotovo automatski. Vaši "
"palčevi bi se trbebali odmarati nad tipokom za razmak, jedinom tipkom za "
"koju će te ih koristiti pri kucanje bez gledanja tastature. Ostali prsti bi "
"trebali biti položeni na tri susjedne tipke markirane tipke centralnog red. "
"Tipke za iste prste su grupisane skupa po bojama. Pokušajte ne pomjerati "
"ruke i uvijek vratiti prste na njihove pozicije za odmor nakon što ste "
"utipkali karakter."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Start typing the text in the middle of the screen. The next key you have to "
"press is always highlighted on the keyboard visualization. While you type "
"you may make mistakes and hit the wrong key. In that case the characters "
"will displayed in red and you have to hit &Backspace; as often as necessary "
"to erase the wrongly typed characters."
msgstr ""
"Počnite kucati tekst sa sredine zaslona. Slijedeća tipka koju trebate "
"pritisnuti uvijek je označena na prikazu tastature. Dok kucate moguće je "
"napraviti grešku i pritisnuti pogrešnu tipku. U tom slučaju karakteri će "
"biti prikazani crvenom bojom te je potrebno da pritisnete &Backspace; "
"onoliko kuta poliko ste pogriješili kako bi obrisali pogrešno unesene "
"karaktere."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When you have successfully completed a line of text you need to press the "
#| "<keycap>Return</keycap> to advance to the next line."
msgid ""
"When you have successfully completed a line of text you need to press the "
"&Enter; to advance to the next line."
msgstr ""
"Kada ste uspješno unijeli red teksta potrebno je da pritisnete "
"<keycap>Return</keycap> kako bi ste napredovali u naredni red."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The key used to advance to the next line can be changed using <link linkend="
"\"configuration_dialog\">&i18n-ktouch; configuration dialog</link>"
msgstr ""
"Tipka za napredovanje u naredni red može  biti promijenjena koristeći <link "
"linkend=\"configuration_dialog\">&i18n-ktouch; podešavajući dijalog</link>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid "Review your progress"
msgstr "Provjerite svoj napredak"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you have completed a lesson &i18n-ktouch; will switch to the score "
"screen. It displays your current training and lesson statistics and shows a "
"graphical history of previous training sessions."
msgstr ""
"Nakon što ste završili lekciju &i18n-ktouch; će promjeniti zaslon sa "
"rezultatima. On izbacuje vašu trenutnu vježbu i ststistike lekcije te "
"pokazuje grafički historiju vaših prijašnjih vježbi."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:319
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Statistics dialog of &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Statistički dijalog &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Statistics dialog of &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Statistički dijalog &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the statistics dialog you can select to show a particular lesson or "
"<guilabel>All Lessons</guilabel>. This is useful to distinguish between "
"overall performance and skill in certain lessons."
msgstr ""
"U statističkom dijalogu moguće je izabrati prikaz određene lekcije ili "
"<guilabel>All Lessons</guilabel>. Ovo je korisno kako bi ste razlikovali "
"okupan učinak i vještinu u određenim lekcijama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you feel ready for the next lesson press <guibutton>Next lesson</"
"guibutton> button in the toolbar to continue with the next lesson of the "
"current course or <guibutton>Repeat lesson</guibutton> button to try your "
"skills on the current lesson again. The <guibutton>Next lesson</guibutton> "
"button will be only available if you have passed the lesson."
msgstr ""
"Ako se osjećate spremnim za sljedeću lekciju pritisnite <guibutton>Slijedeća "
"lekcija</guibutton> dubme na alatnoj traci kako bi ste nastavili sa "
"sljedećom lekcijom trenutnog kursa ili <guibutton> Ponovite lekciju </"
"guibutton> dugme kako bi ste ponovo okušali svoje vještine na trenutnoj "
"lekciju.  <guibutton> Slijedeća lekcija </guibutton> dugme će biti dostupano "
"samo ako ste prošli lekciju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to switch to some other lesson or course press <guibutton>Return "
"to Home Screen</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Ukoliko želite promjeniti lekciju ili kurs pritisnite <guibutton>Vrati na "
"Početni Zaslon</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you do not want to continue the training with &i18n-ktouch; just close "
"the application window."
msgstr ""
"Ako ne želite nastaviti vježbu sa &i18n-ktouch; samo izađite iz "
"aplikacijskog prozora."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid "Training Preparation"
msgstr "Pripreme za Vježbu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pretty much everything in the &i18n-ktouch; home screen should be self-"
"explanatory. The top toolbar is meant to be the place where you can view and "
"configure &i18n-ktouch; settings. The course selector can be used to view "
"the information about the courses and switch between them."
msgstr ""
"Skoro sve na &i18n-ktouch; početnom zaslonu bi trebalo biti "
"samoobjašnjavajuće. Vrh alatne trake je postavljen tako da ga možete vidjeti "
"i podesiti &i18n-ktouch; postavke. Odabirač kursa može biti iskorišten za "
"pregled informacija o kursu i zamjeni među njima."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-ktouch; toolbar"
msgstr "&i18n-ktouch; alatna traka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The toolbar of &i18n-ktouch; houses the profile button at the left and the "
"application menu button at the right."
msgstr ""
"Alatna traka &i18n-ktouch; udomljava profilno dugme na lijevoj te dugme za "
"aplikacijski meni na desnoj strani."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "Profile management"
msgstr "Upravljanje profilom"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The profile button with the name of your profile at the left of home screen "
"toolbar can be used to manage &i18n-ktouch; profiles."
msgstr ""
"Profilno dugme sa imenom vašeg profila na lijevoj strani vaše trake sa "
"alatima može se koristiti za upravljanje &i18n-ktouch; profilima."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Profile management in &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Upravljanje profilima &i18n-ktouch;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Profile management in &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Upravljanje profilima &i18n-ktouch;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can review the settings of the existing profiles, delete them or create "
"a new profile using <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-list-add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Možete provjeriti postavke postojećeg profila, obrisati ili kreirati novi "
"profil pomoću <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-"
"list-add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> dugmeta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To switch to the review mode press <guibutton>Edit</guibutton>. To select a "
"profile and return to the home screen press <guibutton>Use Selected Profile "
"</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Da bi ste Ušli u mod za provjeru pritisnite <guibutton>Uredi</guibutton>. Da "
"bi ste izabrali profil i vrtili se na početni zaslon pritisnite  "
"<guibutton>Koristi Odabrani Profil </guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Reviewing profile information</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Provjera profilnih informacija</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Reviewing profile information</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Provjera profilnih informacija</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>&i18n-ktouch; menu</title>"
msgstr "<title>&i18n-ktouch; meni</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:412
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; menu can be opened using <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> button in the toolbar of the home screen."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; meni može biti otvoren koristeći <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> dugme na alatnoj traci na početnom zaslonu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
