#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:467
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A shortcut to the &systemsettings; module to configure the keyboard "
"settings. Useful to prepare for training on a different keyboard layout."
msgstr ""
"Kratica &systemsettings; moda za podešavanje ostavki tastature. Korisno za "
"pripremanje vježbe na različitim tipovima tastatura."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On platforms lacking the support for detecting the keyboard layout "
"automatically, especially &Microsoft; &Windows;, this entry is replaced with "
"a submenu to select &i18n-ktouch;'s keyboard layout manually."
msgstr ""
"Na platformama sa nedostatkom podrške za automatsko otkrivanje tipa "
"tastature, posebice  &Microsoft; &Windows;, ovaj ulaz je zamijenjen sa "
"podmenijem za odabir &i18n-ktouch; tipa tastature ručno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:483
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&i18n-ktouch; will open a standard &kde; save dialog. Description of this "
#| "dialog in details can be found in the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
#| "files.html\">Opening and Saving Files</ulink> chapter of the &kde; "
#| "Fundamentals."
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu item, for "
"more information read the section about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
"menus.html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; će otvoriti standardni &kde; dijalog za snimanje. Detaljan "
