"html\">Otvaranje i Snimanje Fajlova</ulink> dijela &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration dialog"
msgstr "Podesi Dijalog"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can customize &i18n-ktouch; quite a bit. The settings apply for all "
"profiles globally. Open the configuration dialog by pressing "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button at the right of "
"the top toolbar of the home screen then choosing <guimenuitem>Configure "
"Typewriting Trainer...</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; možete prilično prilagoditi. Postavke se primjenjuju globalno "
"za sve profile. Otvorite podešavajući dijalog prtiskajući "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> dugmetom na gornjoj "
"desnoj strani alane trake početnog zaslona te birajući <guimenuitem>Podesi "
"Pomoćnika za Kucanje na Tastaturi...</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:501
#, no-c-format
msgid "Training Settings"
msgstr "Postavke za Vježbe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this dialog you can select the options that control tutor window "
"appearance and how &i18n-ktouch; behaves during training."
msgstr ""
"U ovom dijalogu možete odabrati opcije koje upravljaju izgled prozora za "
"vježbu i kako se &i18n-ktouch; ponaša prilikom vježbe."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:506
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Training options</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Mogućnosti vježbe</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Training options</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Mogućnosti vježbe</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:513
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Enforce correction of typing errors</guilabel> check box can "
"be used to control whether typing errors have to be corrected."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>primorava ispravke grešaka pri kucanju</guilabel> dok se kontrolna "
"kutija može koristit za upravljanje bilo kojih grešaka koje želite ispraviti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can control the visibility of statistics and keyboard panes during "
"training using <guilabel>Show keyboard</guilabel> and <guilabel>Show real-"
"time statistics</guilabel> check boxes."
msgstr ""
"Možete upravljati vidljivošću statistika i okana tastature za vrijeme vježe "
"koristeći <guilabel>Pokaži tastaturu</guilabel> i <guilabel>Pokaži "
"blagovremene statistike</guilabel> kontrolne kutije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:521
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The keystroke to go to the next line of training text can be chosen from "
#| "two options, <keycap>Return</keycap> or <keycap>Space</keycap>."
msgid ""
"The keystroke to go to the next line of training text can be chosen from two "
"options, &Enter; or &Space;."
msgstr ""
"Ključnu tipku za prelaz u slijedeći red teksta za vježbu možete izabrati iz "
"dvije mogućnosti <keycap>Vrati</keycap> ili <keycap>Razmak</keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:525
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Lesson unlocking limits</guilabel> can be used to choose "
"settings that control unlocking of higher level lessons. &i18n-ktouch; "
"checks the given limits at the end of each level and decides whether to "
"unlock the next lesson. If the typing speed in characters per minute and "
"correctness are <emphasis>both</emphasis> above or equal to the "
"<guilabel>Lesson unlocking limits</guilabel> &i18n-ktouch; will unlock the "
"next higher level lesson."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Otključavanje granice za lekciju</guilabel> može se koristiti za "
"odabir postavki koje kontrolišu otključavanje lekcija višeg nivoa. &i18n-"
"ktouch; provjerava zadane granice na kraju svakog nivoa i odlučuje šta da "
"otključa u slijedećoj lekciji.Ukoliko je brzina kucanja u karakterima po "
"minuti i tačnosti su <emphasis>both</emphasis> veći ili jednaki  "
"<guilabel>Otključavanje granice za lekciju </guilabel> &i18n-ktouch; će "
"otključati slijedeći viši nivo lekcija."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color Settings"
msgstr "Postavke Boje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:539
#, no-c-format
msgid "In this dialog you can tweak the colors used by &i18n-ktouch;."
msgstr ""
"U ovom dijalogu možete malo promjeniti boju koje koristi &i18n-ktouch;."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Color settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Postavke boje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Color settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Postavke boje</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:548
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can select the background color for each finger keys."
msgstr "Možete odabrati pozadinsku boju tipke za svaki prst."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid "Course and lesson selection"
msgstr "Odabir kursa i lekcije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:559
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; automatically detects your keyboard layout and shows only the "
"courses optimized for this layout."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; automatski otkriva vaš tip tastature i pokazuje optimalne "
"kurseve za vaš tip."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On some platforms, especially &Windows;, keyboard layout auto-detection is "
"not available. Use the application menu to select your keyboard layout "
"manually."
msgstr ""
"Na nekim platformama, naročito &Windows;, automatsko određivanje tipa "
"tastature je nedostupno. Koristite aplikacijski meni kako bi ste odabrali "
"vaš tip tastature ručno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:570
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switching courses"
msgstr "Mijenjanje kurseva"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Should there are more than one course available for your keyboard layout you "
"can choose your favorite one using <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-arrow-left.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> and <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-arrow-right.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> buttons to the right of the label with course name. If "
"there is only one course the buttons won't be visible."
msgstr ""
"Ako postoji više od jednog dstupnog kursaza vaš tip tastature možete "
"izabrati vaš preferirani koristeći <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-arrow-left.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> and <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-arrow-right.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> dugmadi koje se nalaze desno od naljepnice sa imenom "
"kursa. ukoliko postoji samo jedan kurs dugmadi neće biti vidljive."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:582
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unlocking lessons"
msgstr "Otključavanje lekcija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:583
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have chosen <guilabel>I have no or only very little experience in "
"machine typing</guilabel> during <link linkend=\"creating_profile\">initial "
"profile creation</link> you will find that some lessons are locked. These "
"items are marked with <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-object-locked.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> icon and cannot be accessed until you pass the previous "
"lessons."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste odabrali <guilabel> Imam nimalo ili jako malo iskustva sa kucanjem "
"na mašinama</guilabel> za vrijeme <link linkend=\"creating_profile"
"\">početnog kreiranja profila</link> otkit će te da su neke lekcije "
"zaključane. Ove stavke su označene sa <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-object-locked.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> ikonom i ne može im se pristupiti bez "
"završavanja prethodne lekcije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:593
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The settings to pass lessons can be changed using <link linkend="
"\"configuration_dialog\">&i18n-ktouch; configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Postavke oko prolazka lekcije mogu biti promijenjene koristeći <link linkend="
"\"configuration_dialog\">&i18n-ktouch; podešavajući dijalog</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:600
#, no-c-format
msgid "Training on a different keyboard layout"
msgstr "Vježbanje na raznim tipovima tastatura"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With &i18n-ktouch; it is possible to use any keyboard layout for training. "
"Just press the buttons that are highlighted by the trainer, regardless to "
"the labels on your physical keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Sa &i18n-ktouch; moguće je koristit bilo koji tip tastature zavježbanje. "
"Potrebn je samo pritisnuti dugmadi koje je označio pomagač, bez obzira na "
"imena na vašoj fizičkoj tastaturi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:606
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Configure Keyboard...</guimenu></menuchoice> in "
"the application menu to select a different keyboard layout. After that &i18n-"
"ktouch; will adapt accordingly and present you its courses for this layout."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Podesi Tastaturu...</guimenu></menuchoice> u "
"aplikacijskom meniju kako bi ste izabrali drugi tip tastature. Nakon toga "
"&i18n-ktouch; će se prema tome prilagoditi i predstaviti moguće kurseve za "
"odabrani tiptastature."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:612
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On platforms without keyboard layout auto-detection, especially &Microsoft; "
"&Windows;, you have first configure your operating system to use the layout "
"you want to train on and then select the same layout in &i18n-ktouch; via "
"the application menu."
msgstr ""
"Na platformama bez mogućnosti automatskog određivanja tipa tastature, a "
"naročito &Microsoft; &Windows;, najprije morate podesiti vaš operativni "
"sistem da koristi tip tastature na kojem vi želite da vježbate i onda "
"odaberete isti taj tip tastature u &i18n-ktouch; alikacijskom meniju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:624
#, no-c-format
msgid "Efficient training"
msgstr "Vježbe efikasnosti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:626
#, no-c-format
msgid "Training techniques"
msgstr "Tehnike vježbanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:627
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hereafter, you can find some general advice about techniques for learning "
"touch typing."
msgstr ""
"Od sada, možete naći glavne savjete koji se tiču tehnika za učenje kucanja "
"bez gledanja tastature."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:632
#, no-c-format
msgid "Steady speed"
msgstr "Stalna brzina"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:633
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To be efficient when learning touch typing it is important not to simply try "
"to type as fast as possible but to keep a steady speed and find a natural "
"rhythm to press the keys."
msgstr ""
"Da bi ste bili efikasni pri učenju kucanja bez gledanja tastature važno je "
"ne samo da kucate što je brže moguće već i da održavate stalnu brzinu i "
"nađete prirodan ritam za pritiskanje tipki."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:640
#, no-c-format
msgid "Accuracy is a king"
msgstr "Preciznost je kralj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:641
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The next important thing is to focus one's attention on accuracy. Only if "
"you mastered the use of the currently unlocked keys, which means you make "
"only very few errors with them still, you will have chance in the following "
"lessons with even more keys to handle. You will notice you become almost "
"automatically master if you make only very little errors and you will save "
"precious time if you don't have to correct that many errors."
msgstr ""
"Naredna važna stvar je da se usredotočite a preciznost. Ukoliko ste ovladali "
"upotrebu dosad otključani tipki, što znači da pravite jako malo grešaka, "
"dobit će te šansu da u narednim lekcijama koristite još više tipki. Primjeti "
"će te da kako ovladavate kucanjem ako pravite manje grešaka ,štedite "
"dragocjeno vrijeme tako što ne morate ispravljati toliko greška."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:650
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"That is also the reason why the default accuracy level to unlock the next "
"lesson is at 98% while the speed requirements are pretty moderate with just "
"180 characters per minute."
msgstr ""
"Ovo također objašnjava zašto je osnovni nivo tačnosti potreban da otključate "
"novi nivo najmanje 98% dok su zahtjevi za brzinu prilično umjereni sa samo "
"180 karaktera po minuti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:657
#, no-c-format
msgid "Correcting mistakes"
msgstr "Ispravljanje grešaka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:658
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you made mistakes it's important to correct them efficiently. Correcting "
"single characters is almost always slower than correcting the whole word. "
"For the latter you have just to press <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Backspace;</"
"keycombo>, and retype the word. The mental overhead for this is very small. "
"For the first you have to first locate the your mistake, delete precisely to "
"the location of the error, determine the missing part of the word re-type "
"it. This requires way more concentration when retyping the whole word."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste napravili greške važno je da ih efikasno ispravite. Ispravljanje "
"jednom karaktera je gotovo uvijek sporije nego ispravljanje čitave riječi. "
"Za samo jedno slovo potrebno je pritisnuti <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Backspace;</"
"keycombo> , i potovo otkucate riječ. Opći mentalni trošak u ovom slučaju je "
"veoma mali. Za prvi slučaj potrebno je prvo naći grešku, obrisati sve do "
"vaše greške, odrediti preostali dio riječi i ponovo ga otkucati. Ovo "
"zahtjeva mnogo više koncentracije nego samo ponovono otkucavanje cijele "
"riječi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:670
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pausing the training session"
msgstr "Pravljenje pauze usred vježbe"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:672
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatically"
msgstr "Automatski"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:673
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you open any dialog or switch to different application while you are in a "
"training session the training is paused and the timer is stopped until you "
"focus &i18n-ktouch; window again and hit any key."
msgstr ""
"Ako otvorite bilo koji dijalog ili promjenite aplikaciju dok vaša vježba još "
"uvijek traje , vježba je zaustavljena i brojač je zaustavljen sve dok "
"ponovno ne fokusirate &i18n-ktouch; prozor i pritisnete bilo koju tipku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:678
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The training session will also be paused if there will be no activity by the "
"user for five seconds."
msgstr ""
"Vaša vježba će također biti zaustavljena ukoliko ne bude nikakve aktivnosti "
"korisnika pet sekundi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:684
#, no-c-format
msgid "Manually"
msgstr "Ručno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:685
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can pause the current session manually using <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-media-playback-pause.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button in the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Također možete zautaviti trenutnu vježu koristeći <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-media-playback-pause.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> dugme u traci sa alatima."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:691
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you click on <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-"
"go-home.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button in "
"the toolbar &i18n-ktouch; will pause the current session and show an overlay "
"menu with some further actions."
msgstr ""
"Ak pritisnete <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-go-"
"home.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> dugme u "
"traci sa alatima &i18n-ktouch; će zaustaviti trenutnu vjebu i preko tog "
"prozora pokazati meni sa daljnim radnjama."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:699
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&i18n-ktouch; menu on pausing</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&i18n-ktouch; meni pri zaustavljanju</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:703
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&i18n-ktouch; menu on pausing</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&i18n-ktouch; meni pri zaustavljanju</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:711
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tracking the learning progress"
msgstr "Praćenje napretka učenja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:712
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After completing a lesson, you will not return immediately to the home "
"screen. Instead a special summary and statistics screen is shown."
msgstr ""
"Nakon završavanja lekcije, nećete odmah biti vraćeni na početni zaslon. "
"Umjesto toga  bit će vam prikazan poseban sažetak i zaslon sa statistikama."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:717
#, no-c-format
msgid "Speed and accuracy statistics"
msgstr "Statistike brzine i preciznosti"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:719
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Score screen progress page</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Stranica sa rezultatima</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:723
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Score screen progress page</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Stranica sa rezultatima</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:727
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filter per lesson"
msgstr "Filter po lekciji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:728
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With the help of the speed and accuracy statistics page you can review your "
"learning progress and identify your weaknesses."
msgstr ""
"Uz pomoć stanice sa statistikma za brzinu i preciznost možete pregledati vaš "
"napredak u učenju i odrediti vaše slabe strane."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:732
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The statistics data can be filtered by lesson using drop down box next to "
"the <guilabel>Over</guilabel> label. This feature can be useful to control "
"you progress in the current lesson and compare this progress with the "
"progress in other lessons."
msgstr ""
"Podaci o statistikama mogu biti filtrirani koristeći padajuću kutija pored "
"<guilabel>Preko</guilabel> oznake. Ova mogućnost može biti korisna da "
"kontolišete vaš napredak u trenutnoj lekciji i uporedite ga napredkom u "
"prethodnoj lekciji."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:739
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Statistics range drop down menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Padajući meni sa rasponom statistika</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:743
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Statistics range drop down menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Padajući meni sa rasponom statistika</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:746
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additional data about the session can be viewed in overlays. If you hover "
"the mouse cursor on a point on the graph &i18n-ktouch; will show the "
"statistics of the corresponding session."
msgstr ""
"Dodatne informacije o trenutnoj vježbi moguće je pogledati u pekrivajući "
"menijima. Ako kursor miša dovedete iznad  određene tačke na grafiku &i18n-"
"ktouch; će pokazati statistiku odgovarajuće vježbe."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:752
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Progress per lesson</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Napredak po lekciji</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:756
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Progress per lesson</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Napredak po lekciji</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid "Errors statistics"
msgstr "Statistika grešaka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:763
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The score screen can be switched to show errors rate for each key using drop "
"down menu next to the <guilabel>Show</guilabel> label."
msgstr ""
"Zaslon sa ezultatima može biti promijenjen tako da pokazuje broj grešaka za "
"svaku tipku koristeći padajući meni pored <guilabel>Pokaži</guilabel> oznake."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:768
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Switching the statistics mode</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Mjenjanje moda sa statistikama</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:772
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Switching the statistics mode</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Mjenjanje moda sa statistikama</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:775
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this mode, &i18n-ktouch; shows a bar diagram of errors for each key in "
"the last training session."
msgstr ""
"U ovom modu, &i18n-ktouch; pokazuje na traci dijagram grešaka za svaku tipku "
"u posljednjoj vježbi."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:780
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Errors chart by the keys</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Grafik grešaka po tipki</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:784
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Errors chart by the keys</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Grafik grešaka po tipki</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:787
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can switch back to the lessons graph using the same drop down menu next "
"to the <guilabel>Show</guilabel> label."
msgstr ""
"Možete se vratit na grafik lekcije koristeći isti opadajući meni pored "
"<guilabel>Pokaži</guilabel> naziva."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:791
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have passed the lesson you may choose to start training on the next "
"lesson right away by pressing <guibutton>Next lesson</guibutton> in the "
"toolbar. Otherwise you can repeat the current lesson with <guibutton>Repeat "
"lesson</guibutton> or return to the home screen with the remaining button."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste prošli lekciju možete izabrati da odmah započnete novu lekciju "
"pritiskajući <guibutton>Naredna lekcija</guibutton> u traci. Ili možete "
"ponoviti lekciju sa <guibutton>Ponovi lekciju</guibutton> ili se možete "
"vratit na početni ekran sa preostalim dugmetom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:803
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extending &i18n-ktouch;"
msgstr "Proširujući &i18n-ktouch;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:806
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating courses"
msgstr "Kreiranje kurseva"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:807
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can easily create your own training course using the built-in &i18n-"
"ktouch; course and keyboard layout editor. Press <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button at the right of the home screen "
"toolbar then choose <guimenuitem>Course and Keyboard Layout Editor...</"
"guimenuitem>. You can choose open a course file or create an empty course "
"from scratch or using an existing course as a template."
msgstr ""
"Također možete kreirati vlastiti kurs za vježbanje koristeći ugrađeni &i18n-"
"ktouch; kurs i uređivač za tip tastature. Pritisnite <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> dugme na desnoj strani alatne trake "
"početnog zaslona te odaberite <guimenuitem>Kurse i Uređivač Tipa Tastature..."
"</guimenuitem>. Također možete i otvoriti  kurs ili kreirati prazan kurs te "
"ga napraviti po vašoj mjeri ili koristiti ga šablon."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:816
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You cannot edit the built-in courses, even if you have the write access "
#| "to the installation directory."
msgid ""
"You cannot edit the built-in courses, even if you have the write access to "
"the installation folder."
msgstr ""
"Ne možete uređivati ugrađeni kurs, čak iako imate pristup pisanja po "
"instalacijskm direktoriju."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:823
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Course and Keyboard Layout Editor main window</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Glavni Prozor Uređivača Kursa i Tipa Tastature</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:829
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Course and Keyboard Layout Editor main window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Glavni Prozor Uređivača Kursa i Tipa Tastature</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:835
#, no-c-format
msgid "Course properties"
msgstr "Osobine kursa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:836
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The course properties can be chosen using &i18n-ktouch; course creation "
"wizard. To invoke this wizard you should press <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-document-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> "
"</imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button in the toolbar of "
"<guilabel>Course and Keyboard Layout Editor</guilabel> window."
msgstr ""
"Osobine kurs možete izabrati koristeći &i18n-ktouch; čarobnjaka za kreiranje "
"kursa. Da bi ste pozvali čarobnjaka trebali bi ste pritisnuti "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-document-new.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> dugme na traci "
"<guilabel>Uređivač Kursai Tipa Tastature</guilabel> prozora."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:843
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first page of creation &i18n-ktouch; wizard allows you to choose the "
"type of the data. Select <guilabel>Course</guilabel> and press "
"<guibutton>Next</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Prva stranica kreacijskog &i18n-ktouch; čarbnjaka vam dozvoljava da tip "
"podataka. Odaberite <guilabel>Kurs</guilabel> i pritisnite "
"<guibutton>Naredni</guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:848 index.docbook:1228
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Choosing the type</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Odabiranje tipa</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:854 index.docbook:1234
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Choosing the type</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Odabiranje tipa</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:858
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The second page of wizard allows you to choose the title, the keyboard "
"layout and the description of the course."
msgstr ""
"Druga stranica čarobnjaka vam dozvoljava da odaerete ime, ti tastature i "
"opis kursa."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:863
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>New course wizard second page</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Druga strana čarobnjaka za kreiranje novog kursa</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:869
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>New course wizard second page</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Druga strana čarobnjaka za kreiranje novog kursa</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:873
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The course title is important for the quick-select menu entry in the course "
"list and for the statistics."
msgstr ""
"Ime kursa je bitno za biranje brzog meni ulaza u listu kursa i za statistike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:877
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The description should be used to include information about the lesson "
"author and source of lesson data if any. This description can be shown by "
"pressing <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-dialog-"
"information.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"button in the home screen of &i18n-ktouch;."
msgstr ""
"Opis bi trebalo koristiti za uključivanje informacija o autoru lekcija i "
"izvor o podatacima lekcije ukoliko oni postoje. Ovaj opis može biti prikazan "
"tako što će te pritisnuti <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"Icon-dialog-information.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> dugme na početnom zaslonu &i18n-ktouch;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:885
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you finished with entering appropriate values press <guibutton>Next</"
"guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Nakon što ste završili sa unošenjem pripadnih vrijednosti pritisnite "
"<guibutton>Naredni</guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:890
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>New course wizard third page</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Treća strana čarobnjaka za kreiranje novog kursa</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:896
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>New course wizard third page</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Treća strana čarobnjaka za kreiranje novog kursa</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:900
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the third page of wizard you can choose an other course as a template "
"for your course. Select the course from the list and press "
"<guibutton>Finish</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Koristeći treću stranu čarobnjaka možete izabrati neki drugi kurs kao šablon "
"za vaš. Odabirite kurs sa list i pritisnite <guibutton>Završi</guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:906
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>New course editing window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Prozor čarobnjaka za kreiranje novog kursa</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:912
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>New course editing window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Prozor čarobnjaka za kreiranje novog kursa</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:916
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; will open the course editor window prepared to entering your "
"course data."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; će otvoriti spreman prozor uređivača kursa za unošenje vaših "
"podataka o kursu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:923
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding lessons"
msgstr "Dodavanje lekcija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:924
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A course is an ordered set of lessons. To be efficient for learning touch "
"typing the content of the course should meet a few requirements."
msgstr ""
"Kurs je naređeni set lekcija. Kako bi bio efikasan u učenju kucanje bez "
"gledanja tastature sadržajvašeg kursa mora ispunjavati neke uvjete."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:929
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choose a meaningful name for the lesson"
msgstr "Odaberite značajno ime za lekciju"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:932
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "For each level you can specify the new characters/keys in the lesson. It "
#| "is worth to include the new characters in the lesson title. Click on a "
#| "name label in the <guilabel>Lessons</guilabel> list and enter some "
#| "meaningful name."
msgid ""
"For each level you can specify the new characters/keys in the lesson. It is "
"worth to include the new characters in the lesson title. Click on a name "
"label in the <guilabel>Lessons:</guilabel> list and enter some meaningful "
"name."
msgstr ""
"Za svaki nivo možete pobliže odrediti nove karaktere/tipke za lekciju. "
"Vrijedi uključivati nove karaktere u ime lekcije. Pritisnite oznaku sa "
"<guilabel>Lekcije</guilabel> listom imena te unesite značajno ime."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:938 index.docbook:956 index.docbook:976 index.docbook:994
#: index.docbook:1012 index.docbook:1032 index.docbook:1049 index.docbook:1112
#: index.docbook:1128 index.docbook:1145 index.docbook:1164
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rationale"
msgstr "Obrazloženje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:939
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The text you enter as a lesson title will be shown as lesson information "
"text in the home screen course list. It will be much easier for user to "
"choose the lesson if it has a meaningful title."
msgstr ""
"Teks koji unesete kao ime lekcije bit će pokazano u vidu teksta sa "
"informacijama o lekciji na listi kurseva početnog prozora. Za korisnika će "
"biti mnogo lakše da odabere lekciju sa značajnim imenom."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:946
#, no-c-format
msgid "The first lesson should cover the home keys"
msgstr "Prva lekcija bi trebala pokriti osnovne tipke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:949
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Usually a keyboard has two haptic markers for the keys on the second row "
"belonging to the index fingers. These two keys and the three adjacent keys "
"outwards are the home keys. That's <emphasis>asdfjkl;</emphasis> for the US "
"keyboard layout."
msgstr ""
"Uobičajno je da tastatura ima dva upadljiva markera za tipke drugog reda "
"pripadajučih im kažiprsta. Ove dvije tipke i tri susjedne tipke vanjske "
"tipke čine glavne tipke. To važi <emphasis>asdfjkl;</emphasis> za US tip "
"tastature."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:957
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Those eight keys are the start position of each finger. One must internalize "
"the location of these keys first to successfully learn touch typing."
msgstr ""
"Tih osam tipki predstavljaju početne pozicije prstiju. Svako najprije mora "
"da obuhvati mjesto ovih tipki kako bi uspješn počeo sa učenjem kucanja bez "
"gledanja tastature."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:964
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduce two new keys per lesson"
msgstr "Uvodite dvije nove tipke po lekciji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:967
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The unlocking order of keys is not fixed, but usually keys are introduced in "
"pairs belonging to the same finger on both hands. Make your way from the "
"home keys to the ones further away. Thus, the forth row should be introduced "
"at last. Prefer keys for important characters of your language, this may "
"require to bend the introduction pattern a bit. For example in French "
"accents are really important, this warrants a lesson early-on focusing on "
"the accent key alone."
msgstr ""
"Redosljied uvođenja novih tipki nije fiksan, ali obično se uvode tike u paru "
"i to taku da ogovaraju istim prstima obje ruke. Pronađite svoj put do "
"početnih tipki do onih udaljenijih. Stoga, četvrti red bi treba biti uveden "
"posljednji. Forsirajte tipke sa bitnim karakterima za vaš jezik, ovo može "
"zahtjevati da malo zakrivite uvodni šablon. Npr. u Francuskom akcenti su "
"veoma bitni, te ovo nalaže da neke početne lekcije budu fokusirane samo na "
"tipke za akcente."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:977
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If more keys are introduced the trainee might get overwhelmed by the "
"difficulty of the lesson and loose his motivation. Introduce keys for "
"important keys first to able to form real words earlier."
msgstr ""
"Ukoliko je uvedeno više tipki korisnik bi mogao postati slmljen težinom "
"lekcije te izgubiti svoju motivaciju. Uvodite bitne tipke kako bi ste ranije "
"mogli formirati čitave riječi."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:986
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extra emphasis on the new keys"
msgstr "Poseban naglasak na nove tipke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:989
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make sure the characters belonging to the newly introduced keys are the most "
"or at least very frequently used characters in the lesson text."
msgstr ""
"Pobrinite se da su karakteri pripadajućih novih tipki ili najčešće ili u "
"najmanju ruku večinom zastupljeni karakteri u tekstu lekcije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:995
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the trainee passes a lesson he should have mastered the new keys. This is "
"only possible if the lesson contains a significant amount of the new "
"characters."
msgstr ""
"Ukoliko korisnik prođe lekciju trebali bi da je ovladao novim tipkama. Ovo "
"je moguće sam ako lekcija sadrži značajan broj tih novih karaktera."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:1003
#, no-c-format
msgid "Intersperse lessons with new keys with repetition lessons"
msgstr "Razbacajte lekcije sa novim tipkama i ponavljajuće lekcije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1006
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Every two to three lessons add a repetition lesson without any new keys. "
"These should have an even character mix covering all already introduced "
"characters."
msgstr ""
"Svake dvije ili tri lekcije ubacite i ponavljajuću lekciju bez novih tipki. "
"Ovih bi treba biti toliko da ravnomjerno sadrže sve karaktere kako nove tako "
"i stare."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1013
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Such lessons help to strengthen the acquired skills and provide a way to "
"check the overall training level. They are also better suited for repeated "
"training to further improve one's general typing skills."
msgstr ""
"Ovakve lekcije pomažu pri utvđivanju stečenih sposobnosti te vam daju način "
"da provjerite nivo ukupne uvježbanosti. Ovakve lekcije također pomažu tako "
"što pri ponavljanju vježi korisnik poboljšava svoje ukupne vještine kucanja."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:1022
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dedicated lessons for capitalization"
msgstr "Lekcije posvećene samo pisanju velikih slova"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1025
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There should be several lessons focusing sorely on capitalization. Ideally "
"capitalization is introduced in multiple steps: At first only the left "
"&Shift; key, then the right, then both and followed by one or more "
"repetition lessons."
msgstr ""
"Trebalo bi biti par lekcija fokusiranih samo na pisanje velikih slova. U "
"ideanom slučaju pisanje velikih slova je uvedeno u više koraka. U početku "
"samo lijeva &Shift; tipka, onda samo desna , pa obje te jedna ili više "
"ponavljajućih lekcija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1033
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mastering capitalization is the most difficult part of learning touch "
"typing. Therefore extra effort must be spend on these lessons."
msgstr ""
"Savladavanje pisanja vlelikim slovima je njateži dio učenja kucanja bez "
"geldanja tastature. Stoga se mora uložiti dodatan napo pri savldavanju tih "
"lekcija."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:1041
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cover the complete keyboard layout"
msgstr "Obuhvačanje cijelu tastature bilo kog tipa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1044
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This includes characters and symbols accessible via other modifiers than "
"&Shift;. Ideally every character, number and symbol which is printed on a "
"real keyboard should be covered."
msgstr ""
"Ovo uključuje karaktere i simbole klji su dostupni putem drogih podešavača "
"osim &Shift;. U idealnom svaki karakter, broj i simbol koji je naznačen na "
"tastatur bi tebalo obuhvatiti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1050
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The more complete a course is the more the trainee can learn from it. It "
"also keeps the course interesting for already advanced typists."
msgstr ""
"Što je kurs kompletniji to korisnik može više naučiti iz njega. To također "
"čini kurs zanimljivijim za iskusnije korisnike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1059
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-add.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button to add new "
"lesson to the course, <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"Icon-list-remove.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> button to remove selected lesson from your course and "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-arrow-up.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>/<inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-arrow-down.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> buttons to rearrange the lessons in the "
"course."
msgstr ""
"Koristite  <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-"
"add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>dugme za "
"dodavanje novih lekcija kursu, <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"Icon-list-remove.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> dugme za uklanjanje odabranih lekcija iz vašeg kursa i "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-arrow-up.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>/<inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-arrow-down.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> dugmadi za preuređivanje lekcija u kursu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1074
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Delete lessons only with caution. Doing so may reset the unlocking progress "
"of the users of the course. If you are planning to revise a course "
"thoroughly it is usually better to use the existing course as a base for a "
"new one."
msgstr ""
"Lekcije brišite uz oprez. Ovim je moguće resetovati otključani progres kursa "
"korisnika. Ako ste planirali temeljito ispraviti kurs obično je bolje "
"koristiti postojeći kurs kao osnovu za novi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1080
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The content of the lesson can be edited using bottom right edit field. You "
"can copy snippets of the text from your favorite text editor and paste them "
"to this field."
msgstr ""
"Sadržaj lekcije može biti uređen koristeći donje desno polje za uređivanje. "
"Možete kopirati djeliće teksta iz vašeg odabranog uređivača teksta i "
"zalijepiti ih u polje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1085
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-document-"
"open.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button to "
"open a generic text file that will be loaded into the lesson text field."
msgstr ""
"Koristite <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-"
"document-open.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"dugme kako bi ste otvorili generički fajl teksta koji će kasnije biti učitan "
"u prazno polje teksta vaše lekcije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1091
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-format-"
"justify-fill.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
"button can be used to wrap the lesson text. &i18n-ktouch; editor wraps text "
"such that every line of the lesson does not exceed the recommended 60 "
"characters limit."
msgstr ""
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-format-justify-"
"fill.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> dugme može "
"biti korišteno za umotavanje teksta lekcije. &i18n-ktouch; uređivač umotava "
"tekst tako što svaki red lekcije ne prelazi ograničenje od preporučenih 60 "
"karaktera."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1098
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let's assume you want to add a new lesson. There are a few guidelines you "
"may want to consider:"
msgstr ""
"Pretpostavimo da želite dodati novu lekciju. Postoji par smjernica koje "
"trebate razmotriti:"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:1104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Give lessons a descriptive title"
msgstr "Dajte lekcijama opisni naziv"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Name the new characters if there are any or otherwise state what the lesson "
"is about."
msgstr ""
"Imenujte nove karaktere ako oni uopće postoje ili u suprotnom naglasite o "
"čemu je lekcija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Good titles make it easier to find the right course if one wants to train on "
"something specific."
msgstr ""
"Dobri nazivi pomažu pri pronalazku pravog kursa ako želite da vježbate nešto "
"određeno."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:1120
#, no-c-format
msgid "The lesson text should be composed out of real words and sentences"
msgstr "Tekst lekcije treba se sastojati od pravih riječi i rečenica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Optimally a lesson forms a comprehensible contiguous text on a freely chosen "
"subject."
msgstr ""
"Optimalno lekciju formira opsežan neprekidan tekst o proizoljno odabranoj "
"temi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Training with real words and sentences is more effective than with arbitrary "
"random character combinations since that is closer to real typing. And it is "
"more fun."
msgstr ""
"Vježbanje sa pravim riječima i rečenicama je efikasnije nego sa proizvoljnim "
"slučajnim kombinacijama karaktera ošto je to bliže pravom kucanju. I "
"zabavnije je."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:1136
#, no-c-format
msgid "Avoid non-word character combinations"
msgstr "Izbjegavajte kombinacije karaktera koji ne tvore riječi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This may impossible in the very first lessons where only a few characters "
"are available, but as soon as possible only real words should be used. Never "
"use misspelled words."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je možda nemoguće u prvi par lekcija pošto imate samo par karaktera, ali "
"što je prije moguće počnite korisiti prave riječi. Nikada ne koristite "
"nepravilno napisane riječi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Random character combinations are hard to type and are seldom found in day-"
"to-day typing. Misspelled words on the other hand are confusing and have "
"even a negative learning value, since the trainee may memorize the wrong "
"spelling."
msgstr ""
"Nasumične kombinacije karaktera su teže za kucanje i oni su rijetki u "
"svakodnevnom kucanju. Nepravilno napisane riječi su zbunjujuče i imaju "
"nezaduju vas, pošto korisnik mora pamtiti pravilno pisanje riječi."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:1155
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lesson text should be roughly 600 characters long"
msgstr "Lekcije bi trebala imati ugrubo 600 karaktera"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"They may be longer, up to 1200 characters is okay, but shorter lessons "
"should be avoided. This is especially true for repetition lessons."
msgstr ""
"Ona može biti duža, do otprilike 1200 karaktera, ali e bi trebala biti "
"kraća. Ovo je posebno bitno za ponavljajuče lekcije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keeping within this range ensures that a untrained typist (~120 characters "
"per minute) can finish a lesson in five to ten minutes. Longer lessons get "
"frustrating, shorter ones are ineffective."
msgstr ""
"Ostajanje unutar granica sigurava da neiskusni korisnik((~120 karaktera po "
"minuti) može završiti lekciju za 5 do 10 minuta. Duže lekcije su "
"frustrirajuće,a kraće ne pomažu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quality checks in the lesson text editor"
msgstr "Provjere kvaliteta u uređivaču teksta lekcije"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1178
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Quality check in the course editing window</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Prozor za provjere kvaliteta u uređivaču kursa</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1184
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Quality check in the course editing window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Prozor za provjere kvaliteta u uređivaču kursa</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Above is a screenshot of the course editor with one of a problematic lesson "
"loaded showing one of the built-in quality-assurance checks: if a lesson "
"contains characters not available in that lesson, because they are not among "
"the configured new characters of this lesson or any previous one, they are "
"highlighted in red. There is also a check for too long lines resulting in a "
"muted color for the characters behind the allowed column."
msgstr ""
"Gore je snimak zaslona uređivača kursa sa učitanom jednim od "
"problematičnijih lekcija koje pokazuje ugrađeni provjere osiguranja "
"kvalitete: ako lekcija sadrži karakter koji nisu sadržani u toj lekciji, jer "
"nisu među podešenim novim karakterima te lekcije ili prethodne, označeni su "
"crvenom bojom. Postoji i provjera za dužinu reda teksta te je on označen "
"prigušenom bojom za karaktere iza dozvoljene crte."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the left side there is a list over all data files &i18n-ktouch; knows "
"about, built-in and user-created alike. If the user selects a built-in "
"resource the editor will degrade to a simple viewer, though. If the user "
"selects a keyboard layout the program will adapt appropriately."
msgstr ""
"Na lijevoj strani se nalazi lista svih fajlova za koje &i18n-ktouch; zna, "
"ugrađeni i korisnički kreirani fajlovi. Ako korisnik odabere ugrađene "
"resurse uređivač će se degradirati u običan pregledavač.Ukoliko korisnik "
"odabere tip tastature program će se prikladno prilagoditi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1207
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating keyboard layouts"
msgstr "Kreiranje tipa tastature"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can create your own keyboard layouts using built-in &i18n-ktouch; "
"editor. Usually it's best is to start with an existing layout close to the "
"keyboard layout you want to create, and use that as a base for own layout. "
"That way you can avoid a lot of work."
msgstr ""
"Možete kreirati vaš vlastiti tip tastature koristeći ugrađeni &i18n-ktouch; "
"uređivač. Uobičajno je najbolje početi sa već postojećim približnim tipom "
"tastature koji želite kreirati, i koristite ga kao osnovu za vaš vlastiti "
"tip. Na taj način se izbjegava suvišan posao."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1214
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyboard layout properties"
msgstr "Osobine tipa tastature"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The keyboard layout properties can be chosen using &i18n-ktouch; keyboard "
"layout creation wizard. To invoke this wizard you should press "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-document-new.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button in the "
"toolbar of <guilabel>Course and Keyboard Layout Editor</guilabel> window."
msgstr ""
"Osobine tipa tastature mogu se izabrati koristeći &i18n-ktouch; čarobnjaka "
"za kreiranje tipa tastature. Da bi ste ga pozvali potrebno je pritisnuti "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-document-new.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> dugme na traci "
"<guilabel>Uređivač Kursa i Tipa Tastature</guilabel> prozora."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first page of creation &i18n-ktouch; wizard allows you to choose the "
"type of the data. Select <guilabel>Keyboard layout</guilabel> and press "
"<guibutton>Next</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Prva strana kreirajućeg &i18n-ktouch; čarobnjaka vam dozvoljava da izaberete "
"tip podataka. Odaberite <guilabel>Tip tastature</guilabel> i pritisnite "
"<guibutton>Naredni</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The second page of wizard allows you to choose the title and the name of the "
"layout."
msgstr "Druga strana čarobnjaka vam dopušta da naziv i ime tipa tastature."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1243
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>New layout wizard second page</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Druga strana čarobnjaka za kreiranje novog tipa</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1249
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>New layout wizard second page</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Druga strana čarobnjaka za kreiranje novog tipa</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The layout title is important for the quick-select menu entry in the layout "
"list of <link linkend=\"ktouch_menu\">&i18n-ktouch; configuration menu</"
"link> and for the statistics."
msgstr ""
"Ime tipa je bitno za odabir ulaza brzog menija u listi tipova <link linkend="
"\"ktouch_menu\">&i18n-ktouch; podešavajućeg menija</link> i za statistike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The layout name will be used as a name of the layout by &i18n-ktouch; "
"internally."
msgstr "Ime tipa će &i18n-ktouch; koristit interno kao ime tipa."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1262
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>New layout wizard third page</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Treća strana čarobnjaka za kreiranje novog tipa</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1268
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>New layout wizard third page</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Treća strana čarobnjaka za kreiranje novog tipa</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the third page of wizard you can choose other layout as a template for "
"your layout. Select the course from the list and press <guibutton>Finish</"
"guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Koristeći treću stranu čarobnjaka možete odabrati tip kao šablon za vaš tip. "
"Odaberite kurs sa liste i pritisnite <guibutton>Završi</guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1278
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>New layout editing window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Prozor uređivača za novog tipa</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1284
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>New layout editing window</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Prozor uređivača za novog tipa</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; will open the editor window prepared to entering your keyboard "
"layout data."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; će otvoriti prozor uređivača pripremeljen za unos vašeg tipa "
"tastature."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1295
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding keys"
msgstr "Dodavanje tipki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1296
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Use <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-add."
#| "png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> "
#| "<guilabel>Normal Key</guilabel> button to add new normal key or "
#| "<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-add.png"
#| "\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> <guilabel>Special "
#| "Key</guilabel> button to add new special key (modifier keys, "
#| "<keycap>Space</keycap>, &Backspace;, &Tab;, <keycap>Caps Lock</keycap> or "
#| "&Enter;) to the layout. The <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
#| "fileref=\"Icon-edit-delete.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
#| "inlinemediaobject><guilabel>Delete</guilabel> button can be used to "
#| "remove a selected key from your layout. The scale can be changed using "
#| "the slider at the left part of the editor toolbar."
msgid ""
"Use <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-add.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> <guilabel>Normal "
"Key</guilabel> button to add new normal key or <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> <guilabel>Special Key</guilabel> button to "
"add new special key (modifier keys, &Space;, &Backspace;, &Tab;, "
"<keycap>Caps Lock</keycap> or &Enter;) to the layout. The "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-edit-delete.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject><guilabel>Delete</"
"guilabel> button can be used to remove a selected key from your layout. The "
