"<guilabel>Osnovne Tipke</guilabel>dugme da bi ste dodali novu osnovnu tipku "
"ili <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-add.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> <guilabel>Posebna "
"Tipka</guilabel> dugme da bi ste dodali novi poseban karakter (uređivačke "
"tipke <keycap>Razmak</keycap>, &Backspace;, &Tab;, <keycap>Velika Slova</"
"keycap> ili &Enter;) vašem tipu. <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-edit-delete.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> "
"</inlinemediaobject><guilabel>Obriši</guilabel> dugme može biti korišteno za "
"uklanjanje odabrane tipke iz vašeg tipa. Razmjera može biti podešena "
"korištenjem klizača na lijevoj starni trake uređivača."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The properties of individual keys can be edited using the bottom pane of the "
"editor window."
msgstr ""
"Osobine zasebnih tipki mogu biti uređene koristeći donje okno uređivačkog "
"prozora."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1316
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal keys"
msgstr "Osnove tipke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1317
#, no-c-format
msgid "It is easy to change the size or properties of a key."
msgstr "Lagano je promjeniti veličinu ili osobine tipke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Begin by clicking on the key you want to change. This selects the clicked "
"key as the current key."
msgstr ""
"Započnite pritiskom tipke koje želite promjeniti. Ovo odabire pritisnutu "
"tipku kao trenutnu tipku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are now 4 squares on the corners of the key. By dragging these "
"squares, you will be able to drag the key border to a new location. Dragging "
"the whole key allows you to change the key position in the layout."
msgstr ""
"Sada postoje 4 kvadratiča na čoškovima tipke. Tako što vučemo te tipke, "
"možete pomaknuti granice te tipke na novo mjesto. Vučom cijele tipke moguće "
"je promjeniti poziciju tipke u vašem tipu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The numerical characteristics of the key geometry can also be changed using "
"the <guilabel>Geometry</guilabel> section of the pane at the bottom of the "
"editor window."
msgstr ""
"Numeričke karakteristike geometrije tipke se također može promjeniti "
"koristeći <guilabel>Geometrija</guilabel> odabir sa okna na dnu uređivačkog "
"prozora."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1335
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Editing an individual key properties</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Uređivanje zasebnih osobina tipke</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1341
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Editing an individual key properties</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Uređivanje zasebnih osobina tipke</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The bottom pane can also be used to choose finger to press the key and "
"switch the haptic marker for the key."
msgstr ""
"Donje okno također može biti korišteno za odabir prsta i odgovarajuće mu "
"tipke te promjeniti upadljiv marker za tu tipku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1350
#, no-c-format
msgid "Key characters"
msgstr "Karakteri na tipkama"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The characters that will be shown on a key can be changed using the "
"<guilabel> Characters</guilabel> section of the editor bottom pane."
msgstr ""
"Karakteri koji će biti pokazani na tipkama mogu biti promjenjeni koristeći "
"<guilabel> Karakteri</guilabel> odabir donjeg okna uređivača."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1356
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Editing the character position</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Uređivanje pozicije karaktera</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1362
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Editing the character position</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Uređivanje pozicije karaktera</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add a character by pressing <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> button. A selected character can be removed by pressing "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-remove.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> button."
msgstr ""
"Možete dodati karakter pritiskajući <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject> dugme. Odabrani karakter može biti uklonjen pritiskajući "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Icon-list-remove.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> dugme."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also select the position of individual characters on the key by "
"double-clicking in the <guilabel>Position</guilabel> column."
msgstr ""
"Također možete odabrati poziciju zasebnog karaktera na tipki tao što ćemo "
"dva puta na <guilabel>Pozicija</guilabel> kolonu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1381
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modifiers"
msgstr "Podešavaći"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are several modifier keys that can be defined in &i18n-ktouch;. They "
"can be edited as normal keys but it is helpful to know identifier of "
"modifier key to use them as appropriate. The table of modifier keys "
"identifiers is given below."
msgstr ""
"Postoji par podešavača definisanih u &i18n-ktouch;. Oni mogu biti uređeni "
"kao osnovne tipke ali je korisno je znati identifikator ili podešavačku "
"tipku kako bi ih koristili pravilno. Tabela podešavačkih tipki i "
"inedtifikatora je data ispod."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1388
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modifier keys"
msgstr "Podešavačke tipke"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1392
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modifier key"
msgstr "Podešavačka tipka"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1393
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modifier id in &i18n-ktouch;"
msgstr "Pdešavački id u &i18n-ktouch;"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1398
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Alt;"
msgstr "&Alt;"

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:1399
#, no-c-format
msgid "altgr"
msgstr "altgr"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1402
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Shift;"
msgstr "&Shift;"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:1403
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>left_shift</literal> or <literal>right_shift</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>lijevi_shift</literal> ili <literal>desni_shift</literal>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1413
#, no-c-format
msgid "Custom Lessons"
msgstr "Naručene Lekcije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The custom lessons feature allows you to extend your training material in an "
"easy way by choosing some arbitrary text."
msgstr ""
"Opcije naručenih lekcija omogučavaju vam da proširite vaš materijal za "
"vježbu tako što izabire neki proizvoljan tekst."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The custom lessons are gathered in a special course, the <guilabel>Custom "
"Lessons</guilabel> course, always available right next to <link linkend="
"\"picking_a_lesson\">the normal built-in courses</link>."
msgstr ""
"Naručene lekcije su sakupljene u poseban kurs, <guilabel>Naručene Lekcije</"
"guilabel>kursu, uvijek dostupni odmah do <link linkend=\"picking_a_lesson\"> "
"osnovnih ugrađenih kurseva </link>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1424
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Custom lessons course</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Kurs naručenih lekcija</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1430
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Custom lessons course</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Kurs naručenih lekcija</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1434
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This special course mostly acts like any other, training and statistics "
#| "gathering works as usual. Clicking on <guibutton>Create New Custom "
#| "Lesson</guibutton> or the <guibutton>Edit</guibutton> button (for "
#| "existing lessons) brings up a stripped-down version of <link linkend="
#| "\"adding_lessons\">the normal lesson editor</link>."
msgid ""
"This special course mostly acts like any other, training and statistics "
"gathering works as usual. Clicking on <guibutton>Add New Lesson</guibutton> "
"or the <guibutton>Edit</guibutton> button (the pencil icon for existing "
"lessons) brings up a stripped-down version of <link linkend=\"adding_lessons"
"\">the normal lesson editor</link>."
msgstr ""
"Poseban kurs je uglavnom kao i svaki drugi, sakupljanje vježbi i statistika "
"radi kao i inače. Pritiskajući <guibutton>Kreiraj Nove Naručenu Lekciju</"
"guibutton> ili <guibutton>Uredi</guibutton> dugme (Za postojeće lekcije) "
"spušta ogoljenu verziju <link linkend=\"adding_lessons\">osnovnog uređivača "
"lekcija</link>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1442
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Custom lesson editor</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Uređivač naručenih lekcija</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1448
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Custom lesson editor</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Uređivač naručenih lekcija</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1452
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The editor will highlight problematic sections of your lesson texts. "
#| "Characters which can't by typed on your keyboard layout will be shown on "
#| "a dark red, lines which are considered to be too long use a gray font for "
#| "the excess characters."
msgid ""
"The editor will highlight problematic sections of your lesson texts. "
"Characters which can't by typed on your keyboard layout will be shown on a "
"dark red background, lines which are considered to be too long use a pink "
"background for the excess characters. &i18n-ktouch; requires that every line "
"of the lesson does not exceed the recommended 60 characters limit."
msgstr ""
"Uređivač će označiti porblematične dijelove vašeg teksta lekcije. Karakteri "
"koji se ne mogu otkucati na vašem tipu tastature će biti prikazani na tamnim "
"crvenim linijama za koje se smatra da su preduge za korištenje sivog fonta "
"za pristup karakterima."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1456
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guibutton>Done</guibutton> button to confirm your edits or close "
"the editor window to cancel them."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1460
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All custom lessons are stored per profile and keyboard layout individually. "
"Use this to manage different sets of lessons depending on the specific "
"training situation."
msgstr ""
"Sve naručene lekcije su smještene po profilu i tipu tastature zasebno. Ovo "
"možete iskoristiti za upravljenje setova lekcija u ovisnosti o specifičnoj "
"situaciji u vježbi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1467
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sharing your results"
msgstr "Dijeljenje vaših rezultata"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1468
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to save your courses and keyboard layouts in separate files "
"outside of the local &i18n-ktouch; database."
msgstr ""
"Moguće je snimiti vaše kurseve i tipove tastature u odvojene fajlove izvan "
"lokalne &i18n-ktouch; baze podataka."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1473
#, no-c-format
msgid "Export/Import"
msgstr "Izlaz/Ulaz"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1474
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To export a course or keyboard layout in a separate file choose the "
"corresponding item in the list at the left part of <guilabel>Course and "
"Keyboard Layout Editor</guilabel> window and press <guibutton>Export</"
"guibutton> button in the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Kako bi ste poslali kurs ili tip tastature na izlaz u zasebnim fajlovima "
"odaberite odgovarajuće stavke sa liste lijevog <guilabel>Uređivač Kursa i "
"Tipa Tastature</guilabel> prozora i pritisnite <guibutton>Izlaz</guibutton> "
"dubme sa trake."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; will open a standard &kde; save dialog. Description of this "
"dialog in details can be found in the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/files."
"html\">Opening and Saving Files</ulink> chapter of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-ktouch; će otvoriti standardni &kde; dijalog za snimanje. Detaljan "
"opis ovog dijaloga moguće je pronaći u <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/files."
"html\">Otvaranje i Snimanje Fajlova</ulink> dijela &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1484
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can choose the name and the location of the &XML; file to be saved."
msgstr ""
"Možete odabrati ime i lokaciju na koju želite da &XML; fajl bude snimljen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1487
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you find it worth to share your files with over users, please send them "
"with some description to <ulink url=\"mailto:kde-edu@kde.org\">kde-edu "
"mailing list</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Shvatit će te da je vrijedno dijeliti svoje fajlove sa  drugim korinicima, "
"molimo da ih pošaljete sa nekim opisima na <ulink url=\"mailto:kde-edu@kde."
"org\">kde-edu mailing listu</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1493
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Your data should be licensed under <ulink url=\"http://www.gnu.org/"
#| "licenses/gpl-2.0.html\">GNU General Public License, version 2</ulink> to "
#| "include them into the default &i18n-ktouch; installation."
msgid ""
"Your data should be licensed under <ulink url=\"https://www.gnu.org/licenses/"
"gpl-2.0.html\">&GNU; General Public License, version 2</ulink> to include "
"them into the default &i18n-ktouch; installation."
msgstr ""
"Vaši podaci bi prebali biti licencirani <ulink url=\"http://www.gnu.org/"
"licenses/gpl-2.0.html\">GNU Generalna Javna Licenca, verzija 2</ulink> kako "
"bi bili uključeni u osnovnu &i18n-ktouch; instalaciju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To import your data files into &i18n-ktouch; press <guibutton>Import</"
"guibutton> button in the toolbar and choose &XML; file that was earlier "
"exported using &i18n-ktouch;."
msgstr ""
"Da bi ste unijeli vaše fajlove sa podacima u &i18n-ktouch; pritisnite "
"<guibutton>Ulaz</guibutton> dugme sa vaše trake i odaberite &XML; koji je "
"ranije poslan na izlaz koristeći &i18n-ktouch;."

